==Tips==
*[[Beer glass]]es can be made using the [[Crafting]] skill or obtained by searching the shelves in the house that the [[apprentice]] and Aadeela the Sorceress are in.
*It is possible to get into the gardens by using [[Thieving]] [[Temporary skill boosts|boosts]], such as those from the juices themselves.
*The elementals can only "see" and teleport the player when there are two squares between them and the player.

